  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was still maybe about 10 miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But from [INAUDIBLE] and I went to-- and on the way, we decided, you know, we separated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hershel, ?] and from all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I don't know if we could survive, you know, both.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, it's a long story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, one time, I-- I hit him, I blood his nose, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe on account of this, and we had-- we had to crawl into another house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he could lift me to crawl in through the window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lifted him, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- it's a big [? story. ?] So we divided.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- Did you think your chances of surviving were better if you were alone?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- I think it was better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if we-- maybe we wouldn't have survived, both of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
